{"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Class","externalID":"c:@M@ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK@objc(cs)SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration","role":"symbol","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration"}],"symbolKind":"class","fragments":[{"text":"class","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK"}],"title":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration"},"variants":[{"paths":["\/documentation\/scanbotdocumentscannersdk\/sbsdkbasescannerenergyconfiguration"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}]},{"paths":["\/documentation\/scanbotdocumentscannersdk\/sbsdkbasescannerenergyconfiguration"],"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}]}],"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/documentation\/ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration"},"kind":"symbol","primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"tokens":[{"kind":"attribute","text":"@objcMembers"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"class"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"SBSDKBaseScannerEnergyConfiguration"}],"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["swift"]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"overview","level":2,"text":"Overview","type":"heading"},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The device did not register significant motion for this period.","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"No positive scanner results have been registered during this period."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Once in energy save mode the device can only return to performance mode if it is moved significantly or a positive"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"detection\/scanning result was registered."}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"orderedList"}]}],"sections":[],"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"The energy management configuration object for a ‘SBSDKBaseScannerViewController’ and its subclasses."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"‘SBSDKBaseScannerViewController’ and subclasses sport a customizable energy management system."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Since scanners running on a live video feed can put a lot of load onto the CPU and\/or GPU"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of the device, causing the battery to drain quickly and running the device hot, you can customize the energy"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"consumption using this class by configuring the rate of detections\/recognitions per second in performance mode as"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"well as in energy saving mode."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"In performance mode the scanners will be fed with a higher, configurable rate of"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"video frames per second."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"After a certain, configurable period of inactivity the energy save mode will be engaged and the rate"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"of scans will be reduced to a lower (configurable) rate."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"You can also configure the time of inactivity before the automatic mode switches from performance to energy save mode."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"Inactivity here means that both of the following conditions are met:"}],"relationshipsSections":[{"kind":"relationships","title":"Inherits From","type":"inheritsFrom","identifiers":["doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/objc(cs)NSObject"]},{"kind":"relationships","title":"Conforms To","type":"conformsTo","identifiers":["doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/objc(pl)NSObject","doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/s7CVarArgP","doc:\/\/net.doo.ScanbotDocumentScannerSDK\/s28Cus